":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25616b4188bca77aa12c5a8c0bd5e57a62655360","tid":1357593,"uid":84088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"969caa4bd9a8e4c86955dacb43086001e24ff80b","tid":1357593,"uid":53915,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f0fd5ff16c83680f2bf0870941a0e6d21c543a96","tid":1357593,"uid":84088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:13:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:14:52.000Z","msg":"我唔係想搞分化<br />\n只係想大家團結 <br />\n元朗都好重要<br />\n我只係唔想元朗人比人當condom <br />\n<br />\n我都講句sorry<br />\n殘體字不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請見諒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:25:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:26:17.000Z","msg":"我地其實唔係以民鬥民，我地係對抗緊「政警鄉黑」， 政、警都比我地搞到無哂辦法，點解我地唔去埋最後一關？（明顯係主線），當中聯辦都叫唔郁依班黑勢力，我地贏面極大，反對我地既力量亦都大大減少，可以專注對抗中共！"},{"pid":"1be74601d82d1029a3b2689ab4f150c98d6c67f3","tid":1357593,"uid":7764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T22:51:24.000Z","msg":"add oil"}]}